	Bug 673894 - Adding events to Google Calendar is broken (Milan Crha)
	Bug 674257 - Recheck attachment availability on message download
	             (Milan Crha)
	Bug 674309 - Crash when calling oauth_init_nss() from two threads
	             (Milan Crha)

