Evolution-Data-Server 1.5.5, 2006-01-16
----------------------------------------

Bugzilla bugs fixed (see http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi):

	#321812 √¢¬Ä¬ì crash during Draft saving in offline mode (Shreyas)
	#314841 √¢¬Ä¬ì gw: Don't Mark Trash As New Messages (Parthasarathi)
	#323570 √¢¬Ä¬ì gw: Forward Of Multiple Messages At Once Loses Formatting (Parthasarathi)
	#320898 √¢¬Ä¬ì gw: Inserted Images Appears As Broken Link Image (Parthasarathi)
	#303998 √¢¬Ä¬ì In 'Exchange Connector' GAL should be selected for 'Autocompletion by default (Sushma)
	#323115 √¢¬Ä¬ì --force-shutdown does not shutdown e-d-s (Harish)
	#326060 √¢¬Ä¬ì Exchange password expiry handling is broken (Sushma)
	#267402 √¢¬Ä¬ì can not specify https URL for a remote calendar location (Tony Tsui)
