	  (Harish)
	- Optimize calendar attachment retrievals (Chenthill) 
	- Fix miscellaneous compiler versions (Harish)
	- Use read cursors request instead of getQM calls in GW backend (Chen)
	- Improve Junk Mail Handling support (Vivek)
